INSERT INTO `wiki_page_content` VALUES (24, 24, '1\r\n⾃我介绍\r\n⾯试\r\n⾃我介绍\r\n学校介绍\r\n家乡介绍\r\n实习经历介绍\r\n实习经历介绍（新）\r\n职业发展规划\r\n职业发展规划/为什么选择加⼊⻄云\r\n项⽬介绍\r\n优势/ 你⽐别⼈强在哪\r\n项⽬中遇到的困难/成就感的事情\r\n项⽬\r\n加⼊富达的理由\r\n个⼈兴趣爱好\r\n我的优势和弱势\r\nAI的看法\r\n反问\r\nThank you so much for the interview opportunity today. My name is Cui Xinshuo.  I will graduate \r\nfrom Liaoning Petrochemical University with a major in Computer Technology in 2024.  \r\nAlong with my undergraduate career, I was not a computer related major but I took self-study \r\ncomputer courses like data structures, operating system, algorithms, and  actively participated in \r\ncomputer-related competitions  winning six national-level awards。 I also took part in server \r\n⾯试\r\n⾃我介绍\r\n2\r\nJAVA development projects，among which a springboot-based teaching reform system has been \r\nused in my school 3 years. \r\nDuring my graduate studies, I did some internships at Dalian Yihui Technology, DXC Technology \r\nand ShouQi YueChe, where I play a role as a Java developer.  These experiences have improved \r\nmy development and design abilities in JAVA and related skills. I think these abilities will help me \r\nto be better at my new job. Hope to join you. Thank you for your listening.  \r\n⾯试官您好，我叫崔新铄。⽬前就读于辽宁⽯油化⼯⼤学计算机技术专业，预计2024年毕业。很荣幸参\r\n加此次⾯试。\r\n在我的本科⽣涯中，我专业排名第⼀，除此之外⾃学了计算机的课程，⽐如数据结构，操作系统，算法\r\n等，还积极参加各种计算机类⽐赛，获得了6项国家级奖项和7项省级奖项。我还参与了⼏个校内的开发\r\n项⽬，如基于Winform的HAZOP分析系统、基于Unity3D的漫游系统和基于Springboot的教学改⾰系\r\n统，该系统已经在学校内部使⽤。\r\n在我研⼀期间，我的专业排名第七，并发表了⼀篇SCI⼆区论⽂。研⼆期间。我分别在⼤连医汇科技和\r\nDXC Technology以JAVA实习⽣的身份进⾏实习，在医汇科技参与开发前置机数据抽取⼯具并监控其在\r\n⽣产环境的运⾏情况，参与设计与开发经营分析平台，并且负责云HIS项⽬的⼀键式部署；在DXC期间参\r\n与了内部笔试系统的设计与开发和索尼数据仓库ETL⼯具迁移⼯作。 \r\n在学校和在外实习的这些经历不仅让我对JAVA的使⽤更为熟练，并很⼤程度上锻炼了我的解决问题的能\r\n⼒。\r\n以上是我的⾃我介绍，谢谢您的倾听\r\njava实习⽣\r\n我就读的学校是位于辽宁省抚顺市的辽宁⽯化⼤学。学校创建于1950年，是中华⼈⺠共和国第⼀所⽯油\r\n⼯业学校。学校设施⻬全，包括体育馆、游泳池、各种球场，学校图书馆是辽宁省最⼤的图书馆。学校\r\n积极倡导雷锋精神育⼈理念，培育浓厚的校园⽂化，营造培养创新⼈才的氛围，每年围绕这些主题举办\r\n不同的活动。这些活动开阔了学⽣的视野，提⾼了他们的道德修养。因为地处辽宁，学校⾥有很多辽宁\r\n美⻝，⽐如沈阳鸡架、锦州烤⾁，尤其是抚顺的特⾊麻辣，别具⻛味。\r\n学校介绍\r\n3\r\nThe school I am studying at is Liaoning PetroChemical University, located in Fushun City, \r\nLiaoning Province. Founded in 1950, it is the first petroleum industry school in China. The school \r\nhas complete facilities, including a gymnasium, swimming pool, and various sports fields. The \r\nschool library is the largest in Liaoning Province. The university actively promotes the spirit of Lei \r\nFeng in education, cultivates a strong campus culture, and creates an atmosphere for fostering \r\ninnovative talents. Every year, various activities are organized around these themes. These \r\nactivities broaden students\' horizons and enhance their moral upbringing. Because of the \r\nlocation of our school --Liaoning, the school offers a wide variety of Liaoning cuisine, such as \r\nShenyang chicken rack and Jinzhou roasted meat. Particularly famous is Fushun\'s Spicy mix. \r\nDalian is a city with a mild and pleasant climate. It has four seasons, but none of them are too \r\nextreme. The winter is not too cold, and the summer is not too hot. It has plenty of sunshine and \r\nfresh air. It’s like living in a natural greenhouse. Dalian is also a famous tourist city that has many \r\nattractions for tourists who love the sea, such as Jinshitan, a resort area with a golden beach \r\nand a geological park, and Xinghai Square, the largest square in Asia. I am a person who loves \r\nthe sea very much. Whenever I have time, I go to see the sea. I really enjoy watching the waves \r\nhitting the beach and feeling the sea breeze, which helps me relieve stress. \r\n在我的实习经历中，我有幸参与了三个不同公司的JAVA后端开发⼯作。⾸先是在⼤连的医汇科技进⾏实\r\n习，期间我主要参与开发前置机数据抽取⼯具、设计与开发医院经营⼤数据分析展示平台以及部署云HIS\r\n项⽬。通过这段实习，我对企业JAVA后端开发的流程和技术有了⼀定的了解。 \r\n接着，在DXC Technology实习期间，我参与了⼀个⾮常有挑战性的项⽬，即让我带领其他实习⽣从零开\r\n始设计和开发部⻔内部笔试系统。这个系统被应⽤于DXC Technology DDC部⻔的内部招聘笔试过程\r\n中。在这个项⽬中，我负责了系统的架构设计和后端开发⼯作。通过与团队的协作和努⼒，我们成功地\r\n完成了系统的开发并投⼊使⽤。\r\n让我对JAVA开发流程以及⼀些技术栈有了更深⼊的了解。 \r\n最后，在北京的⾸汽约⻋实习期间，我主要参与了派单系统的开发⼯作。我负责设计和实现了⾃动半径\r\n功能、乘客排队功能以及即时单抢单功能。同时，我还参与了派单配置中⼼的迁移和升级⼯作，这⼀系\r\n家乡介绍\r\n实习经历介绍\r\n4\r\n列的⼯作经验为我提⾼了JAVA开发⽔平，让我更加熟悉了后端开发的流程和技术，除此之外还了解了\r\nToB和ToC产品的不同。 \r\n通过这三段实习经历，我不仅提升了⾃⼰的技术能⼒，还学会了与团队合作、解决问题和承担责任。这\r\n些经历让我对JAVA后端开发有了更深⼊的理解，相信这些技能也会为我未来的⼯作提供帮助。 \r\n我参加三段实习⾸先是⼤连医汇科技这是我第⼀份实习 这份⼯作中主要是了解了⽣产项⽬中JAVA的开发\r\n流程，之后在DXC Technology进⾏了为期近⼀年的实习，该段实习在技术上我对Linux和Unix的使⽤更\r\n为熟悉，在⼯作⽅法上⽂档撰写更为规范，以及提升了⼀些项⽬管理的能⼒。\r\n最后在⾸汽约⻋⻅识了⼤型的企业级微服务项⽬，并且学到了⼀些在⾼并发场景下的解决⽅案，也让我\r\n在编写代码时考虑的会更为全⾯。\r\n⾸汽约⻋进⾏了为期三个⽉的实习，⾸先第⼀个⽉主要是协助开发派单业务内部的配置中⼼，第⼆个⽉\r\n开始因为技术达标，所以我独⽴维护配置中⼼的重构⼯作，并参与⼀些简单的派单线上功能开发，第三\r\n个⽉参与设计和开发派单⾃动半径功能的开发 解决了运⼒少的城市搜索慢的问题 \r\nFor my internships, I had three different experiences. Firstly, I worked at Dalian YiHui Technology, \r\nwhich was my first internship. In this state, I primarily learned about the Java development \r\nprocess in business projects. \r\nNext, I interned at DXC Technology for almost a year. During this internship, I became more \r\nfamiliar with Linux and Unix. I also learned to write documentation more effectively and improved \r\nmy project management skills. \r\nLastly, I had an internship at Shouqi Yueche, where I worked on a large-scale enterprise micro-\r\nservices project. I learned some solutions for handling high-concurrency scenes \r\nDuring my three-month internship at Shouqi Yueche, the first month involved assisting in the \r\ndevelopment of an internal configuration center for dispatching orders. In the second month, I \r\nbecame proficient in the JAVA development and independently maintained the refactoring work \r\nof the configuration center. I also participated in the development of some simple core \r\ndispatching features. In the third month, I was involved in designing and developing the \r\nautomated radius feature for dispatching orders, which resolved the issue of slow search in cities \r\nwith limited transportation. \r\n实习经历介绍（新）\r\n5\r\n我的职业发展规划是从技术、业务以及语⾔三个⽅⾯进⾏考虑的。\r\n在技术⽅⾯，我计划在⼯作的前1-3年内，进⼀步深⼊学习已有的开发⼯具和常⽤框架的底层\r\n原理。这将帮助我更好地理解它们的运作机制，提⾼开发效率，并能够更好地解决问题。同\r\n时，我也会跟随技术发展，学习新⼯具或框架，保持⾃⼰的技能时刻更新。  \r\n在业务⽅⾯，我会深⼊了解公司的产品、服务和业务流程，以便更好地为产品团队提供⽀持。\r\n语⾔⽅⾯，坚持每⽇的英语学习，争取⼀年左右能够流利沟通\r\nOkay,here is my answer \r\nMy career plan for the next 3 years mainly focuses on three aspects: technical, business, and language. \r\n● I think it is still a process of gaining relevant experience and skills within the first three years. So In \r\nterms of technical skill , I plan to deepen my understanding of the framework we used like Spring、\r\nRedis et all in the first 1-3 years of work.  This will help me better comprehend their operation, improve \r\ndevelopment efficiency, and enhance problem-solving abilities. Additionally, I will keep learning new \r\ntools or frameworks to keep my skills updated. \r\n● Regarding the business aspect, The first 3 years I think is a process  to be familar with the  industry. \r\nSo I should learn as much as possible. So I aim to gain a thorough understanding of the company\'s \r\nproducts, services, and business processes to better support the product team. \r\n● On the language front, I am persisting· in daily English learning and aim to achieve speak fluent in \r\nabout a year. \r\nFor more than 5 years,I believe that my technical level and business understanding have greatly \r\nimproved, so I look forward to lead a team to develop something new which can bring more business \r\nvalue to the company. \r\n我对云计算领域充满了热情和好奇⼼，我希望在未来的3年内能够在这个领域取得突破性的进步。\r\n我是⼀个喜欢探索新事物并且乐于尝试的⼈，每当遇到⼀个新技术，我都会想要亲⾃去体验和学习\r\n它。云计算作为当今软件⾏业的发展趋势和创新驱动⼒，吸引了我⽆数的⽬光。我认为云计算不仅\r\n能够提供⾼效、灵活、可扩展的计算资源，还能够⽀持各种复杂和多样的应⽤场景，为⽤户带来更\r\n好的体验和价值。\r\n职业发展规划\r\n●\r\n●\r\n●\r\n职业发展规划/为什么选择加⼊⻄云\r\n6\r\n在我的实习经历中，我曾经使⽤过⼀些云计算产品，例如AWS的EC2，阿⾥云的轻量服务器等，\r\n但是这些只是冰⼭⼀⻆，还有很多更深⼊和⼴泛的云计算知识和技能等待着我去探索和掌握。我认\r\n为⻄云作为AWS在中国的技术⽀持，拥有⼴阔的平台，能够让我接触到最前沿和最实⽤的云计算\r\n技术。因此，我期望通过加⼊⻄云，成为⼀名优秀的技术⽀持⼯程师，在未来的3年内对AWS的各\r\n个产品都有⼀定的了解，因为我认为只有⾃⼰熟悉，才能为客户提供⾼质量和⾼效率的技术解决⽅\r\n案。同时，我也会利⽤这个平台不断地提升⾃⼰的技术⽔平和业务能⼒，争取在云计算的各个领域\r\n都有所提升。\r\nI am passionate and curious about the field of cloud computing, and I hope to make \r\nsignificant progress in this area within the next three years. I am someone who enjoys \r\nexploring new things and is eager to try them out. Whenever I encounter a new technology, \r\nI want to personally experience and learn it. Cloud computing, as the current trend and \r\ninnovation driver in the software industry, has captivated my attention countless times. I \r\nbelieve that cloud computing not only provides efficient, flexible, and scalable computing \r\nresources but also supports various complex and diverse application scenarios, bringing \r\nbetter experiences and value to users. \r\nDuring my internship experience, I have used some cloud computing products such as \r\nAWS\'s EC2 and Alibaba Cloud\'s lightweight server. However, these are just the tip of the \r\niceberg, and there is much deeper and broader cloud computing knowledge and skills \r\nwaiting for me to explore and master. I believe that NWCD, as the technical support for \r\nAWS in China, has a broad platform that allows me to access the cutting-edge and \r\npractical cloud computing technologies. Therefore, I aspire to join NWCD and become an \r\nexcellent technical support engineer, gaining a certain understanding of various AWS \r\nproducts within the next three years. I believe that only by being familiar with them can I \r\nprovide customers with high-quality and efficient technical solutions. At the same time, I \r\nwill continuously improve my technical skills and business capabilities through this \r\nplatform, striving for improvement in various fields of cloud computing. \r\n1. ⾃动半径\r\n项⽬介绍\r\n7\r\n原有半径是通过算法组返回来，然后根据算法接⼝的结果进⾏搜素。 但是存在的问题就是算法计\r\n算需要时间，经常就要触发保底策略（3公⾥） ，但是⼀些运⼒少的城市，3公⾥内没有司机的概\r\n率很⼤，因此⽆论搜索多少轮都会是⽆效操作，导致司机搜索的效率不是很好，因此我跟周围同事\r\n以及产品讨论，考虑做⼀个平滑扩⼤搜索范围的功能，最终设计了⼀个根据搜索轮数去扩⼤搜索半\r\n径的功能，该功能上线后，运⼒少的城市搜索轮数减少，司机响应率增加。\r\n2. 配置中⼼迁移\r\nS：旧的配置中⼼很多功能是写死的维护不⽅便，因此重新做了个⼀个新的配置中⼼ 基于\r\nSpringboot+Vue的 \r\nT \r\nA \r\nR \r\n说到优势我认为⾸先就是我有强⼤的⾃信⼼，我认为别⼈能做到的事情，只要我努⼒我也能做到，\r\n我本科是⾮计算机